title: DAZ3D - POSER - WATER SPRING (THE REAL ONE)
description:
This water spring is located in the lowland, in a cool place, where the shadows play on the stones, and the sky and plants are reflected in the surface of the water.

Perhaps this is mysterious place wherever night fairies fly and water spring is illuminated by magic light.

As bonus this pack contains an Iray scene subset with materials of flowers for Night lighting.

This scene includes different groups of objects. For example you can quickly and easy turn off/on trees, bushes, flowers and plants or move its.
